        <activityName xml:lang="en">raffinate to generic market for residual hydrocarbon mix, from steam cracking operations</activityName>
        <includedActivitiesStart xml:lang="en">The activity starts with the reception of raw materials at the factory gate.</includedActivitiesStart>
        <includedActivitiesEnd xml:lang="en">The activity ends with the production of residual hydrocarbon mix, from steam cracking operations for the generic market.</includedActivitiesEnd>
        <generalComment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">This is a linking activity which links the product raffinate to the generic market for residual hydrocarbon mix, from steam cracking operations. All chemicals that enter this market provide the function of a fuels.</text>
        </generalComment>
      </activity>
